  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td class=&#34;tg-9l91&#34;&gt;Summary:&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td class=&#34;tg-60hs&#34;&gt; In the spirit of Halloween, this talk explores our fascination with extraterrestrial life — from little green men and UFOs to what science actually says about the possibility of intelligent life beyond Earth. We trace how our idea of “aliens” has evolved through pop culture and real astronomy, touching on Roswell, the Wow! Signal, and why the universe’s silence might be the spookiest mystery of all...&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td class=&#34;tg-9l91&#34;&gt;Date &lt;/td&gt;
